{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 10 shows an image sample from the BRODEN dataset.",
    "CelebA-CelebFaces Attributes DatasetCelebA [170] is a large celebrity image face sample with over 200 K samples, annotated with 10,177 identities, 40 labels face attributes (e.g.",
    "Bald, Bangs, Big_Lips, Big_Nose, Black_Hair), and 5 landmark locations (e.g.",
    "lefteye_x, lefteye_y, nose_x, nose_y).",
    "All image samples in Fig. 11 were resized to 128 * 128 pixels aligned in the image centre."
  ]
}